		BUITRAGO, Valentina Agudelo<sup>1</sup>; HARDT, Letícia Peret Antunes<sup>2</sup>; OLIVEIRA, Paulo Ritter de<sup>3</sup>; HARDT, Carlos<sup>4</sup>		<BR>
